      <title>读书笔记 《一个悲观主义者的积极思考》</title>
      <link>https://yuqiteng.github.io/posts/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%82%B2%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%AF%E6%9E%81%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/</link>
